S.FORM: I 1956 a miheca saka 3 folad saka 1 a romi'ad masofoc ci Dalia Grybauskaitė , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Lithuania anini i ci Dalia Grybauskaitė, patirengan a romi'ad i 2009 a miheca saka 7 folad saka 12 a romi'ad.
